			<h3 ><a href="#p28">Re: 4.0 Observations - Feral (Bear)</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=28#p28"><img src="./styles/thedruidsgrove/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=74">Felkan</a></strong> &raquo; Tue Oct 19, 2010 5:40 pm </p>

			

			<div class="content">It is my understanding that the new swipe is provides just enough threat to keep mobs off healers.  Anyone else doing AoE DPS is gonna pull.  I also read that you should avoid Maul unless you just have a butt load of rage as it is no longer as good as it use to be.<br /><br />Read Kalon's <a href="http://wowthinktank.blogspot.com/2010/10/bear-faq-for-401cataclysm.html" class="postlink">Bear 4.0 FAQ</a> for more details.</div>

			

		</div>

		
