			<h3 ><a href="#p34">Re: 4.0 Observations - Feral (Bear)</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=34#p34"><img src="./styles/thedruidsgrove/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=59">Sildan</a></strong> &raquo; Wed Oct 20, 2010 6:49 pm </p>

			

			<div class="content">Good stuffs.<br />The threat just above healers though I don't believe to be the case yet. In the next patch they are supposedly cutting swipe down to 15 rage and cutting the damage and threat in half without adjusting the 6 second CD. The tanks being just above healer agro is their dream for the future. That was from Big Bear Butt Blogger.</div>

			

